name: CoinSale Token
description: CoinSale is a decentralized in app launchpad that allows users to launch their own token and Non-fungible token(NFT) .We are the world's first in-app launchpad, where users can launch any chain token and NFT securely through the app.Our app is built in a decentralized manner and is more secure for everyone.We have brought this with the safety of all users in mind, project owners and investors can participate in the launchpad without any third-party support. Investors don't have to enter any phishing link and connect wallet to join launchpad.
